Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  门是开的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏的时候不许进谷仓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来啊  你们这些二货
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该上床了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  游戏结束了  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧  10分钟前就熄灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些小混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我数到十
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们再不出来我要抽你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是闹着玩的
